sentences: Dylan Carlson (born March 12, 1968) is an American musician, best known as the guitarist and founder of the drone metal/post-rock group Earth, and the main contributor to his solo project Drcarlsonalbion.
From 1991 to 1996, Earth had an ever-changing lineup.
Carlson attributes a lack of (full-length) studio album recordings from 1997 to 2005 to "legal and drug problems".
He now lives in recovery of heroin addiction.
